Educational Use Notice:
This project is designed as an educational tool for teaching Python programming
to children through 3D world building. Feel free to use, modify, and share this
project for educational purposes. We encourage teachers, parents, and students to
adapt this code for their learning needs.

Attribution:
While not required by the MIT license, we'd appreciate attribution if you use
MadMine in educational materials or derivative projects. A simple "Based on
MadMine by Tom" is sufficient and helps others discover this educational tool.